      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DAVOLAS LEGACY NZ (10) made it two wins from this row in her last four appearances when she came from this barrier to get home by 3.4 metres at Menangle last week. Building a handy record here and with even luck she can make it two on the trot. CHARLIES ACE NZ (7) draws for a trail and is a leading player backing up off a placing at Menangle on Tuesday. GOODTIME BRAVO (8) is in good form and is working towards a win having finished second at his latest appearance, beaten a neck. Should enjoy a nice smother from this draw and if he gets the gaps he is a hope. ROCKSIE ROCK (9) raced wide in his last-start fourth at Menangle. That continued his good form, highlighted by a Goulburn win last month. Go well.",
